<font color="#FF0000">VIETNAM THOUGHTS</font><br>
<tt>Mon Dec  2 14:42:02 US/Eastern 1996
</tt><p>
I was in Vietnam from 11/67 to 11/68 with the USAF. During this period I experienced manner different emotions which still effect me to this day. There is not a day that goes by that I don't think of my time in NAM. My hope is that this country never makes this kind of mistake again. I continuely<br>
advise anyone who will listen of the many mistakes we made by starting and continueing the war. It will be up to a generation who have not experienced war to keep us out of another Vietnam.<br><br>
WELCOME HOME TO ALL THE VIETNAM VETS !!!!<br><br>
KEITH F. KELLEY<br>
Chapter 451 VVA
